San Ardo Union Elementary Dashboard DA Summary

Report Purpose

This report is created to synthesize information to assist San Ardo Union Elementary in reflecting on the student groups for whom indicators led to Differentiated Assistance.

Latest Status by Group

The graphic below shows the color for each student group for each indicator from the dashboard. This reflects the latest available colors from the 2022 dashboard. Please note that this also includes student groups with 11-29 students for whom data is available but status is not used for accountability purposes.

Qualifying Groups

This table displays which student groups qualified the district to be eligible for Differentiated Assistance. Moreover, for each student group it shows which Priority Areas and associated indicator criteria for which the student group qualifies.
